        {
            "title": "財經｜小鵬汽車(09868)上季轉賺3.8億人民幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜小鵬汽車(09868)上季轉賺3.8億人民幣\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜小鵬汽車(09868)上季轉賺3.8億人民幣</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小鵬汽車(09868)公布，截至去年12月底止虧損11.39億元(人民幣‧下同)，每股虧損0.6元，不派末期息；2024年同期虧損57.9億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">期內，總收入767.19億元，按年升87.73%。按非公認會計原則，經調整虧損4.58億元，2024年經調整虧損55.5億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單計去年第四季，盈利3.83億元，首次在單季度錄得正淨收益；2024年同期虧損13.3億元。季度總收入為222.5億元，按年增加38.2%</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-64680bde-234f-3b26-9769-8c7934466d5f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">小鵬汽車副董事長及聯席總裁顧宏地表示，2025年第四季度，小鵬汽車的毛利率達到21.3%，再創新高，淨利潤達到3.8億元，公司通過以技術領先驅動的商業模式，達成了與傳統車企迥異的盈利路徑。去年底，公司在手現金476.6億元，為其堅定投入物理AI研發提供了堅實的保障。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於2026年第一季度，公司預期汽車交付量將介乎6.1萬至6.6萬輛，按年減少約29.79%至35.11%。總收入將介乎122億至132.8億元，按年跌約16.01%至22.84%。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%B0%8F%E9%B5%AC%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A-09868-%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%A3%E8%BD%89%E8%B3%BA3-8%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-095855219.html",
